N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 649.4 - Exclusive agreements prohibited

State Regulations

Effective September 1, 1990, providers of intrastate
operator assisted communications services shall not take any action or enter
into any arrangement which restricts end-user selection among competing
interexchange telephone corporations or end-user access to competing providers
of intrastate operator assisted communications services, or pay any commissions
or other compensation to any entity engaged in such action or
arrangement. Notes
